{"tid":236224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【即時入獄】褻瀆伊斯蘭教罪成 華裔省長鍾萬學判囚2年","createTime":"2017-05-09T14:42:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T13:04:26.000Z","uid":20058,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4014723aa5169866abf6476145959f1fefe13c26","tid":236224,"uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:42:41.000Z","msg":"印尼耶加達華裔基督徒省長鍾萬學被指侮辱《可蘭經》，法院周二判他褻瀆伊斯蘭教罪成，判囚兩年，即時入獄，鍾萬學計劃提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n法官指出，鍾萬學「在法律上令人確信他犯下褻瀆罪行，因此我們判處他兩年監禁」。審訊期間，有數百名伊斯蘭教團體成員在法院外聚集要求重判，市內各處分別有支持和反對他的人集會，警方嚴陣戒備防止衝突。<br />\n鍾萬學去年在一次演講中指摘對手扭曲《可蘭經》某句經文，「愚弄」穆斯林不能選出異教徒當領袖，有人認為他此舉是褻瀆《可蘭經》，令伊斯蘭團體不滿爆發多次示威。他本人已道歉，在風波擾攘於上月競逐連任失敗。<br />\n路透社  <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170509/56670018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170509%2F56670018&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=615d55cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170509%2F56670018&h=1258f202\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170509/56670018</a>"},{"pid":"2e0b3cc939c5876f595efce14860ff7bfaacdbe1","tid":236224,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53619492accc4a2c93dcfb6536856f004d31359c","tid":236224,"uid":104088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T15:00:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1b362842ea8310979ee7073236c10389ae0d032","tid":236224,"uid":2818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T15:01:40.000Z","msg":"有宗教法國家都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ba78e8225c6d58dee8d129fe666beb511becba3","tid":236224,"uid":24140,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"